    "body": "Are you looking for something like the [palette feature ](https://starship.rs/config/#prompt) or something else?:\n\n```toml\n# Set 'foo' as custom color palette\npalette = 'foo'\n\n# Define custom colors\n[palettes.foo]\n# Overwrite existing color\nblue = '21'\n# Define new color\nmustard = '#af8700'\n```",
